member.name: T:Cobisi.Net.IProxyClient
member.summary: Defines methods to establish proxied connections to a proxy server.

member.name: M:Cobisi.Net.IProxyClient.Connect(System.Net.IPEndPoint,System.Net.IPEndPoint)
member.summary: Create a new proxied socket and connects it to the given endpoint, passing through the configured proxy server.
member.param: The local endpoint used to bind the new proxied socket.
The target endpoint for the proxied connection.

member.name: M:Cobisi.Net.IProxyClient.ConnectExisting(System.Net.Sockets.Socket,System.Net.IPEndPoint)
member.summary: Connects an existing socket to the given endpoint, passing through the configured proxy server.
member.param: The existing socket to use while establishing the proxied connection.
The target endpoint for the proxied connection.
